## 📊 Visualizations Created

- Age Distribution Histogram
- Category-wise Sales Chart
- Gender Distribution Pie Chart
- Top Cities Analysis
- Product Distribution
- Quantity vs Total Sales Scatter Plot
- Correlation Heatmap

---

## 🗄️ SQL Business Questions

- Top 5 Products by Revenue
- Sales by Category
- Top Cities by Revenue
- Gender-wise Orders
- Average Customer Age
- Monthly Sales Trend
- Total Orders

---

## 📈 Dashboard

A static dashboard was created in Microsoft Excel to present:

- Total Orders
- Average Customer Age
- Top Category
- Top Product
- Sales Charts
- Customer Distribution

---

## 📌 Key Insights

- Electronics generated the highest revenue.
- Laptop was the highest revenue-generating product.
- Patna generated the highest revenue.
- Average customer age is **41.36 years**.
- Total orders processed: **1000**.

